## Working in this project

This project uses the `research` skill in proposition-first mode. Hypothesis generation state lives under `propositions/Pxxx_slug/`: observations create generated doubts, generated doubts create working propositions, working propositions create expected consequences, proposition status determines whether a derived hypothesis is allowed, and each derived hypothesis owns one hypothesis plan under `hypotheses/Hxxx_slug/plan.md`.

Plans declare a category and mode; plans are checked before execution with `research-plan-review`, results are analyzed after execution with `research-result-analysis`, and claims are recorded in the hypothesis plan. State-changing decisions are not global iteration notes: project-wide decisions stay in top-level `decisions.md`, proposition decisions stay in `propositions/Pxxx_slug/decisions.md`, and hypothesis decisions stay in `propositions/Pxxx_slug/hypotheses/Hxxx_slug/decisions.md`.

Research scripts should run through `new_run.py` and leave evidence under `propositions/Pxxx_slug/hypotheses/Hxxx_slug/experiments/runs/<run_id>/`. Print-only output is not a completed result: stdout is not evidence. Each completed run needs `run_manifest.json`, `logs/stdout.log`, `logs/stderr.log`, and at least one manifest-listed durable artifact in `outputs/`, `tables/`, `figures/`, or `intermediate/`. Run `check_run_artifacts.py` before using a run for Result analysis, observations, claims, decisions, or reports.
